es bring extreme results. If you want a normal life, do what normal people do. If you want to know God intimately, walk with Him daily, and please Him in every way, you''re going to have to do what few do. Absolutely nothing.', 3962, 0), (75914, 'Trump victory makes me realized, That you don''t really need people option to be come a winner.', 15938, 0), (75915, 'NASA astronauts have only managed to live continuously on the International Space Station (ISS) for a year and Biosphere 2 on Earth failed at two years of uninterrupted human habitation. Both cases required extracting the sickened people from the toxic environments. At this point it is ludicrous to talk about a permanent manned base on Mars.', 5008, 0), (75916, 'Those people make us strong and then valuable, whom we do not like initially.', 8568, 0), (75917, 'If we want people to accept us as we are, then we should accord the same courtesy to them', 11007, 0), (75918, 'I must not expect everyone to act or think like I do as God has created each of us differently.', 11007, 0), (75919, 'People will react to you as a result of their own mindset, rather than as a reflection of your worth. Most people use others as mirrors for their own darkness. If you have been hurt by such people, perhaps you can use these experiences to become a different kind of person—one who reflects the light within others instead of using them as mirrors. Maybe your experiences of pain can lead you to being a great leader, someone who lights up the world. Your most painful struggle is ripe with opportunity.', 5084, 0), (75920, 'There is no window to look outside.There is no window to look within.Open the doors.', 5935, 0), (75921, 'We encounter souls, not bodies.', 15939, 0), (75922, 'For America is composed not of two sorts of people, but of two frames of mind - the first engaged in doing what is would like to do, the second pretending that such things do not exist.', 97, 0), (75923, 'Normal people live distracted, rarely fully present.